data.title: Prince Gustaf Adolf and Princess Margaret of Connaught wed

data.meta_description: Prints of The royal wedding of Prince Gustaf Adolf of Sweden and Princess Margaret of Connaught
data.text:
The royal wedding of Prince Gustaf Adolf of Sweden and Princess Margaret of Connaught. After the ceremony, the princess takes back her bouquet from her sister, Princess Patricia.

15th June 1905. Mary Evans Picture Library makes available wonderful images created for people to enjoy over the centuries. Â© Mary Evans Picture Library 2015 - https://copyrighthub.org/s0/hub1/creation/maryevans/MaryEvansPictureID/10433810
